The clip was posted on Facebook by Andre Snyman of Blockwatch who shared: Watch how a man shoots his girlfriend dead. This happened in Durban this week. The guy has handed himself over to the police. WARNING: NOT FOR SENSITIVE VIEWERS I can confirm that she worked for us. She died on Tuesday evening on our premises said a woman who works for C. Steinweg Logistics.She could not confirm whether the woman was killed by her boyfriend. All we know is she was familiar to him. The woman who asked not to be named would not be drawn into more details.She did not know how long the woman had been working for the company.Police had not confirmed the shooting nor the arrest at the time of publication.